{"tid":2051182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国留美學生趁火打劫　示威炫耀戰利品名牌袋","createTime":"2020-06-04T14:49:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T03:55:55.000Z","uid":184679,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"1b832d41fdfe61a67a9889056b1a4c3ecca06d28","tid":2051182,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T14:49:58.000Z","msg":"全美各地因為非裔美國人佛洛伊德之死引發了示威抗議變成暴動，許多示威抗議者甚至趁火打劫。一位疑似是中國大陸留美學生袁宏睿2日在社群網站上PO文，炫耀他搶劫來的名牌精品如DIOR、GUCCI等，還嗆聲：「熱愛祖國。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/06/04/2592396-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F06%2F04%2F2592396-XXL.jpg&h=290624be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲中國留美學生袁宏睿。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n不久後有網友爆料，這名25歲的袁宏睿，目前正在美國西雅圖求學。<br />\n<br />\n袁宏睿PO文炫耀，嗆聲這些名牌「你們窮人買不起。」還自詡是熱愛祖國的表現。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/06/04/2592393-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F06%2F04%2F2592393-XXL.jpg&h=b1a553ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n袁宏睿除了公開在社群網站炫耀自己搶劫而來的精品圖片，還大言不慚的說：「在西雅圖搶的GUCCI包包，好看嗎？」他甚至還嗆網友「可以去FBI舉發」。他說：「美國人還欠我們中國很多帳沒還！幾個包包而已，美國人幹嘛那麼小器？」<br />\n<br />\n他還說：「明天再去搶一波，我先吃個飯。臉皮這種東西真的不重要，要是中共願意資助我，我就可以煽動示威者，把美國變成第二個香港，想想都刺激。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/06/04/2592395-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F06%2F04%2F2592395-XXL.jpg&h=5e98f64e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=756168\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D756168&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5EudgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=addd4367\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D756168&h=55ccc6e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=756168</a>"},{"pid":"f